dcterms:description: The LPBA dataset contains 40 brain MRI volumes, each with 54 manually labeled regions of interest (ROIs). All volumes have been rigidly pre-aligned to mni305, with 30 volumes used for training and 10 for testing.
dcterms:title: LPBA

dcterms:creator: A. Klein
J. Tourville
dcterms:description: The Mindboggle dataset consists of brain MRI volumes that have been affinely aligned to mni152, containing 62 manually labeled ROIs. It includes 42 volumes for training and 20 for testing.
dcterms:title: Mindboggle

dcterms:description: The Abdomen CT (ABCT) dataset contains CT volumes with annotations for four organs: liver, spleen, left kidney, and right kidney. It has undergone canonical affine pre-alignment and includes 35 volumes for training and 8 for testing.
dcterms:title: Abdomen CT (ABCT)
